H1.text: What is the capital of Guyana. New Amsterdam

H2.text: What is the capital of Guyana. Linden

H3.text: What is the capital of Guyana. G-town

A4.text: Georgetown is the capital and largest city of Guyana.

A5.text: All executive departments of Guyana's government are located in the city, including Parliament Building, Guyana's Legislative Building and the Court of Appeals, Guyana's highest judicial court.
